args.code:
import PyPDF2

pdf_path = './13-DecBound/DecBound-main/paper.pdf'
text = ''
with open(pdf_path, 'rb') as f:
    reader = PyPDF2.PdfReader(f)
    for page in reader.pages[:5]:  # Read first 5 pages for context
        text += page.extract_text() + '\n'
print(text[:2000])
